<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_269_r1l32"><expan>Regenſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_269_r1l35"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Vns hat fürgelegt fraw Kathreẏ des Criſtan vvolcʒhofers 
<del rend="strikethrough"> in</del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l36">
<add>elıche wirtin</add> wie ſie derſelb 
<del rend="strikethrough">Criſtan wolcʒhofer </del> Jr wirt an dem leipgeding das ſıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_269_r1l37">von ew hab / gen ew hinder daʒ Jr das niht <expan>geuolge<ex>n</ex></expan> künne <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_269" id="134r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Regensp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt
                                                  fraw Kathrey, des Cristan Wolczhofers,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>,
                                                  <add>eliche wirtin</add>, wie sie derselb ir wirt
                                                  an dem leipgeding, das sie von ew hab, gen ew
                                                  hinder, daz ir das niht
                                                  <expan>gevolge<ex>n</ex></expan> künne.<expan>
                                                  Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz.</del><app>
<note><q type="endnote">...</q>Text bricht hier ab.</note>
</app></ab>
</div>
